Define Project Scope and Features
Clearly outline the features your vegetable sales app and website will have.

✅ User Features:

Browse vegetables with images, descriptions, and prices

Search, filter, and sort products

Add to cart and checkout with online payment

User authentication (Login/Register)

Order tracking with real-time updates

✅ Admin Features:

Add, edit, or remove vegetables

Manage orders and delivery status

View sales reports

✅ Delivery Features:

Assign delivery agents

Track order delivery status
